Ranger Help for: make fish trap
================================

SYNTAX:      make fish trap
USAGE:       Any terrain to craft; water terrain to set
SLOT COST:   4
BASE SP:     48
SKILL TYPE:  creation / survival

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to weave a collapsible fish trap from
wildcraft supplies. The Ranger needs 2 binding fiber and 1 kindling.

Once made, carry the trap to a river, lake, sea, beach, swamp, or
underwater area and use:

  set fish trap
  check fish trap
  retrieve fish trap

Checking a ready trap adds a fish catch to your camp stores. Fish
catches can be used by 'camp cook fish stew' and 'camp cook hunter
feast' at your camp.
